trans-unit.source: Indicates when events and other life-cycle events occur while a <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpApplication" /> request is being processed.
trans-unit.target: Indica cuándo se producen eventos y otros eventos de ciclo de vida durante el procesamiento de una solicitud <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpApplication" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> enumeration is used with the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.CurrentNotification%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> class to determine what event in the pipeline is currently processing.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> enumeración se utiliza con la <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.CurrentNotification%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> clase para determinar qué eventos de la canalización se está procesando actualmente.

trans-unit.source: To determine when all the handlers for a specific event of the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instance have finished processing, use the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.IsPostNotification%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Para determinar cuándo todos los controladores de un evento específico de la <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instancia ha finalizado el procesamiento, use la <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.IsPostNotification%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> type is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> tipo se introdujo en la [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/includes/net-v35-long-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> enumeration with the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.CurrentNotification%2A> property to determine which event of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instance is processing the request.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se muestra cómo utilizar el <xref:System.Web.RequestNotification> enumeración con la <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.CurrentNotification%2A> propiedad para determinar qué evento del elemento actual <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instancia está procesando la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AcquireRequestState" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.BeginRequest" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.BeginRequest" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the handler that is mapped to the requested resource is being invoked to process the request.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se está invocando el controlador asignado al recurso solicitado para que procese la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.LogRequest" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.LogRequest" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.MapRequestHandler" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.MapRequestHandler" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates a point in the application life cycle just before the handler that processes the request is mapped.
trans-unit.target: Indica un punto en el ciclo de vida de la aplicación justo antes de que se asigne el controlador que procesa la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.ReleaseRequestState" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.ReleaseRequestState" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.ResolveRequestCache" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.ResolveRequestCache" /> para la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that processing of the request is complete and that the response is being sent.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha completado el procesamiento de la solicitud y que se está enviando la respuesta.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.UpdateRequestCache" /> event was raised for the request and is processing.
trans-unit.target: Indica que se ha producido y se está procesando el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.HttpApplication.UpdateRequestCache" /> para la solicitud.
